  <div id="text-content_23A864C0-38E2-0139-BDBF-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>When using the Rich Content Editor, you can resize the window manually or expand the entire Rich Content Editor to fullscreen view.</p>
  </div>
</div>

    <div class="html-embed">
  <iframe width="560px" height="320px" allowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay *" title="Canvas Shorts: How do I resize the Rich Content Editor (RCE)?" src="https://community.instructuremedia.com/embed/e94bda14-37e5-49d5-9931-24a0563a978f" frameborder="0"></iframe>
